title: Finn Balor Returns From Injury At Live Event, Triple H Also Returns In Main Event (Videos, Photos)
text:
â€” WWE (@WWE) March 11, 2017 
As seen above in the video posted by WWE, RAW Superstar Finn Balor made his return to action at tonight's WWE live event in Buffalo, New York. Balor teamed with Sami Zayn and WWE United States Champion Chris Jericho to defeat the returning Triple H, Samoa Joe and Kevin Owens. Balor has been out of action since SummerSlam 2016 when a shoulder injury forced him to relinquish the WWE Universal Title the next night on RAW. No word yet on Balor's plans for WrestleMania 33 but he's expected to work the show.
